fastREST Server
===============

Dependencies
------------

* autotools and libtool
* Various Boost Libraries

Build instructions
------------------

    autoreconf -i -f
    ./configure
    make
    make install

External components
-------------------

fastREST internally uses the following components :

boost.m4
https://github.com/etiam/boost.m4

rapidjson 0.11
https://code.google.com/p/rapidjson/

